### Get the Data
```{r}

average_cost <- read_csv("2022-W18/average_cost.csv")
wind  <- read_csv("2022-W18/wind.csv")
solar  <- read_csv("2022-W18/solar.csv")
capacity  <- read_csv("2022-W18/capacity.csv")
```
### Neccessary libraries
```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(readxl)
library(skimr)
library(lubridate)
library(scales)
library(grid)
```

